  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This open label, non-interventional study is to show the efficacy of Crestor (rosuvastatin)
      in reduction of LDL-cholesterol and cardiovascular risk parameters in patients with
      hypercholesterolemia. Effectiveness is to be evaluated using the difference in LDL
      cholesterol level between the first and the second visit after 12 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
